data.description: Amazing 2 bedroom, 2 bath town-home with a basement in desirable Smyrna location. The main level’s open floor plan opens to the two-story deck overlooking the private backyard. The living room features a fireplace and the eat-in kitchen has countertops and stainless steel appliances. The master bedroom has a large walk-in closet, vaulted ceilings, and a spacious bathroom with separate jacuzzi tub. The secondary bedroom also has a private full bathroom, making this a great roommate floor plan. Prime location with easy access to I-285 and I-75, area restaurants, parks, and shops. Great opportunity with no HOA and no Rental Restriction!
